text: Blobfish may refer to: *Psychrolutidae, a fish family commonly known as blobfishes **Psychrolutes microporos, commonly known as a blobfish or fathead **Psychrolutes marcidus, commonly known as a smooth-head blobfish or a blobfish **Psychrolutes occidentalis, Western blobfish or Western Australian sculpin * Ebinania macquariensis, Macquarie blobfish, a species of Ebinania
title: Blobfish
